Filters invariants to only those with CFI >= 0.7 (true causal anchors)\r\n3. Compare prediction accuracy against frequency-baseline compression\r\n\r\nFirst, let me examine the current research state to build upon:\r\n\r\n```json\r\n{\"path\": \"research/CFI_RESULTS.md\"}\r\n```\r\n\r\n```json\r\n{\"path\": \"state\"}\r\n```\r\n\r\n```json\r\n{\"path\": \"pulse_2026-03-24 103522.md\"}\r\n```\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 0\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 10:37:40\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774363074887}}
{"type":"message","id":"abf1a4d9","parentId":"5782a3aa","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:38:05.287Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The pulse completed. Let me now read the full pulse log to get the complete details.","thinkingSignature":"390018e6f22e541957cf16034d1321bab52c452cd58fed17ebd6a5295b1bd662"},{"type":"text","text":"**Sandbox Pulse — 2026-03-24 10:37 AM ET**\n\n---\n\n**What happened this cycle:**\n\n- **CFI analysis ran** on the frequency-invariant pool from 20 recent pulses\n- **Key finding:** 44.8% of frequency-invariants are pure noise (CFI=0 — zero causal relevance), and only 5.7% are strong causal anchors (CFI≥0.7). The bulk of persistent tokens are metaprogramming artifacts that survive by coincidence, not causality\n- **Revealed a critical distinction** in the invariants: *Process* tokens (CFI=0, e.g. `on_message`, `reset_persona`) vs *Research Trajectory* tokens (CFI>0.7, e.g. `cfi_analysis`, `sandbox_memory`)\n- **CFI-weighted compression experiment was drafted** — filters to only high-CFI tokens and compares next-pulse prediction quality vs the frequency baseline\n- **Previous mutation rejected** — a draft mutation from the prior pulse was in `proposed/` and got moved to `rejected/` (noted in git as a rename). No applied mutation this cycle\n- **Git auto-committed** — `master 4e39b25` updated with the new session log\n\n**Result:** No new memory mutation applied. The CFI analysis is now the active observation. The next pulse is expected to implement and test the CFI-weighted compression."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2604,"output":326,"cacheRead":12137,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15067,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774363074890}}
